{"tid":1296631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾國斌：對自由黨發稿重申支持修例有保留","createTime":"2019-07-08T12:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T12:18:59.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d03d6224a4d765b913de98440c5711d82e7331","tid":1296631,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:13:31.000Z","msg":"自由黨在6月9日的反修訂《逃犯條例》遊行當晚發新聞稿，重申支持修例。自由黨榮譽主席田北俊批評太倉卒，又指當時黨魁鍾國斌反對出稿。<br />\n<br />\n黨主席張宇人回應指，當晚曾諮詢黨內三位立法會議員的意見，即包括鍾國斌，當時沒有人提出反對。<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌回應時表示，出信一刻他有保留，又認為現時最大問題是特首無回應市民訴求引起不滿，相信改革行會能解決部分社會上的問題。對於黨內有一名行會成員，他認為應該考慮社會責任辭去行會議席。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467284-20190708.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467284-20190708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpeIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=a8be2cb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467284-20190708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=98818208\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467284-20190708.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9779c1d462f59f9a1fc36787355a61b28a99f5f2","tid":1296631,"uid":246586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"一定係啦 過咗成個月都唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44de748394f556753d39bdb4eb5949fd09725253","tid":1296631,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:18:59.000Z","msg":"想割蓆  冇咁易"}]}